---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Paid Ads" description="Google Ads. Facebook Ads. Landing pages. Retargeting. Jobs on demand — when your system is ready for it." currentPage="paid-ads">

    <!-- SECTION 1 — HERO -->
    <section class="section section--hero surface-base noise-bg">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center">
            <div class="col-left-7 stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow);">Step 3 — Turn It Up</p>
                <h1 class="t-display t-display--hero">
                    YOU'VE SPENT MONEY<br />ON ADS.<br />
                    <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow);">DID THEY ACTUALLY WORK?</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    You spent the money. Got clicks. Maybe some calls. But can you tell me exactly how many jobs came from last month's ad spend? Which campaigns? Which keywords?
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 500;">
                    If you can't, you're gambling. Not advertising.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" style="background: var(--theme-accent-yellow); border-color: var(--theme-accent-yellow); color: var(--color-surface-base);">Turn It Up →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-right-5">
                <div style="aspect-ratio: 4/5; background: var(--color-surface-elevated); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <img src="/images/logos/badmouth-logo-stacked.png" alt="Badmouth Digital" style="width: 60%; opacity: 0.15;" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider" style="background: var(--theme-accent-yellow);" />

    <!-- SECTION 2 — PROBLEM -->
    <section class="section section--split section--padded surface-sunken">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-left-7 stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">Why Your Ads Failed</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section">
                    YOUR ADS AREN'T THE PROBLEM.<br />
                    <span class="t-accent t-crt-shake">YOUR SYSTEM IS.</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    You ran Google Ads. Or Facebook Ads. Or both. You got clicks. Maybe even some calls. But the leads vanished. The numbers didn't add up. Nobody could tell you what your cost per job was.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    Because the landing page wasn't built for conversion. The follow-up wasn't automated. The tracking wasn't set up. The ad was doing its job. Everything else wasn't.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-right-5">
                <div class="card stack-3" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-yellow);">
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;">This Only Works When</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Your website converts (Step 1).</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Your follow-up is automated.</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Your tracking is installed.</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Your Google profile is optimized (Step 2).</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-2);">Ads are gasoline. Make sure the engine runs first.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3 — WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
    <section class="section section--padded surface-base">
        <div class="grid-page grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-full text-center stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow" style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow);">Paid Ads Management</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    HERE'S WHAT YOU <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow);">GET.</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-full">
                <div class="inner-grid-3">
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">CAMPAIGN CREATION</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Google Ads. Facebook Ads. Built from scratch for your services, your area, your audience. Not templates.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">LANDING PAGES</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Dedicated pages for each campaign. Built to convert, not to look pretty. One CTA. One job.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">CONVERSION TRACKING</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Every call, form, click — tracked back to the exact ad and keyword. Know your cost per lead and cost per job.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">RETARGETING</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">People who visited but didn't convert see your ads again. Stay top of mind until they're ready.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">FOLLOW-UP AUTOMATION</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Ad lead comes in? System follows up. Text, email, CRM entry. All automatic. No leads fall through.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">MONTHLY REPORTING</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Spend, leads, cost per lead, cost per job. Real numbers. If it's not working, we tell you and fix it.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider" />

    <!-- SECTION 4 — PRICING -->
    <section class="section section--statement section--padded surface-elevated">
        <div class="grid-page grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-content text-center stack-6">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">Pricing</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow);">$2,500</span> / MONTH
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch;">
                    Management fee. Plus your ad spend (you control the budget). Campaign creation, optimization, landing pages, tracking, and reporting — all included.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 500;">
                    Month-to-month. No long-term contracts. Your ads work or you walk.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" style="background: var(--theme-accent-yellow); border-color: var(--theme-accent-yellow); color: var(--color-surface-base);">Request Paid Ads →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 5 — CTA -->
    <section class="section section--cta section--padded section--mic-drop section--mic-drop--yellow has-scanlines" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="grid-page" style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
            <div class="col-content text-center stack-4">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="color: var(--color-surface-base); margin-inline: auto;">
                    STOP GAMBLING.<br />
                    <span class="mic-drop__headline">START INVESTING.</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 50ch; margin-top: var(--space-4);">
                    When the system handles what comes in, ads become an investment with a measurable return. Not a hope and a prayer.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--lg">Turn It Up →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- REINFORCEMENT -->
    <section class="section section--statement section--padded-sm surface-pure">
        <div class="grid-page">
            <div class="col-content text-center">
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 500;">
                    Ads without a system are a money fire. Build the system first. Then turn it up.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>
